  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u00a0\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u00a0\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Unrest in Aton due to non-supply of fuel to health workers",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Unrest erupted at the Aton Sibetco filling station after the health workers who went to get fuel were not given fuel.",
        "However, it has been reported that some people have been waiting in line since yesterday (01) and when they went to get fuel this morning, they ran out of fuel.",
        "Enraged by this, they have joined the protest. As a result, the hospital staff working in areas like Kinikathena, Navalapitti, Thalawakkalai, Kotakalai, Tikoya, Pokavanthalawa and Maskelia were involved in the protest.",
        "It is noteworthy that this protest took place as it was reported that 6,600 liters of petrol had been brought and that it had run out."
      ],
